The paper discusses the QuickXPlain algorithm, which is widely used in various areas such as model-based diagnosis, recommender systems, verification, and the Semantic Web. These areas are typically covered by the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Programming Languages (cs.PL), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
